oMeta.description: Suppressed regularly since its publication, My Secret Life details the erotic experiences of the narrator “Walter,” a Victorian gentleman of wealth and status. Painstakingly detailed, the novel describes his incredible womanizing over several years, which includes his exploits with partners of his own stature as well as prostitutes and those of the lower class.
oMeta.title: My Secret Life
